    Advanced Search Tips
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <ul class="as-tips">
      <li><strong>all</strong> retrieves items that contain every word in this search box, regardless of order.</li>
      <li><strong>any</strong> retrieves items that contain any of the words in this search box, but not necessarily all of them.</li>
      <li><strong>begins with</strong> retrieves items that contain at least one field beginning with the words in this search box.</li>
      <li><strong>phrase</strong> retrieves items that contain all the words in this search box, in this order.</li>
      <li class="mt-3"><strong>AND</strong> retrieves items that contain the words from both rows.</li>
      <li><strong>OR</strong> retrieves items that contain the words from either row.</li>
      <li><strong>NOT</strong> retrieves items that don't include the words from this row.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Rows are processed from top to bottom. Use <strong>OR</strong> before <strong>AND</strong> and <strong>NOT</strong>.</p>
